type="local">Forester 4.0</fr:link> › enhanced XML support</fr:link> › emitting XML and resolving namespaces</fr:link> › a worked example</fr:title><fr:taxon>Example</fr:taxon></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter><fr:p>The following code causes <fr:link
href="jms-00YE.xml"
title="MathML"
addr="jms-00YE"
type="local">MathML</fr:link> to be emitted (in the correct namespace), combining <fr:link
href="jms-00RK.xml"
title="Forester 4.0 › enhanced XML support › emitting XML and resolving namespaces › XML namespace declaration"
addr="jms-00RK"
type="local">Feature <fr:contextual-number
