title="MathML"
addr="jms-00YE"
type="local">MathML</fr:link> to be emitted (in the correct namespace), combining <fr:link
href="jms-00RK.xml"
title="Forester 4.0 › enhanced XML support › emitting XML and resolving namespaces › XML namespace declaration"
addr="jms-00RK"
type="local">Feature <fr:contextual-number
addr="jms-00RK" /></fr:link> and <fr:link
href="jms-00RM.xml"
title="Forester 4.0 › enhanced XML support › emitting XML and resolving namespaces › XML literals"
addr="jms-00RM"
type="local">Feature <fr:contextual-number
addr="jms-00RM" /></fr:link>:</fr:p><fr:pre><![CDATA[\xmlns:mml{http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML}
\<mml:math>[display]{block}{
 \<mml:mrow>{
  \<mml:msup>{
   \<mml:mi>{x}
   \<mml:mn>{2}
  }
  \<mml:mo>{+}
  \<mml:mi>{x}
 }
}]]></fr:pre><fr:p>The above displays as follows:</fr:p><mml:math
display="block"
